  "1150560": {
    "name": "王国：两位君主",
    "steam_appid": 701160,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/aa44bbb3a0b6beb35c6364327449f80a.poster.avif?t=1771343090\" width=1170 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/aa44bbb3a0b6beb35c6364327449f80a.webm?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/aa44bbb3a0b6beb35c6364327449f80a.mp4?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>建造 - 探索 - 保卫 - 征服</i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘的面纱笼罩着这片未知的中世纪大地，古老的纪念碑、遗迹和神话般的生物在此等待你的到来。往昔时代的回音诉说着过去的伟大，<strong>《王国：两位君主》</strong>是屡获殊荣的《王国》系列游戏的一部分，你将作为君主踏上冒险之旅。在这趟横轴冒险旅程中，你将骑上坐骑，征召忠诚的臣民，建设你的王国，同时还得保护王冠不被贪婪生物夺走——这些骇人的怪物满心想着将王国的宝藏偷个一干二净。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独行还是同行 - 在《王国：两位君主》中，两位君主可以携手合作，建立并巩固一个经得起时间考验的王国。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/ed6f4f261162b608a0ba5f28350cf37a.avif?t=1771343090\" width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/d83de48afb9ed95bd874d10b5c08916d.poster.avif?t=1771343090\" width=1170 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/d83de48afb9ed95bd874d10b5c08916d.webm?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/d83de48afb9ed95bd874d10b5c08916d.mp4?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造高耸的城墙和瞭望塔，为强大的王国奠定基础，同时建造农场、征召村民，从而实现繁荣。在《王国：两位君主》中，你可以通过扩大和发展王国，获得新的臣民兵将和技术。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/5af79d41a91923274bf061edb57ac04b.poster.avif?t=1771343090\" width=1170 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/5af79d41a91923274bf061edb57ac04b.webm?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/5af79d41a91923274bf061edb57ac04b.mp4?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索疆域以外的未知之地，穿过偏僻的森林和古老的废墟，寻找宝藏和隐藏的知识，协助你一路冒险。谁知道你会发现什么传奇神器或神话生灵呢？  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/fb4b3a8bfc4bed609c8f0b1853dfca65.poster.avif?t=1771343090\" width=1170 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/fb4b3a8bfc4bed609c8f0b1853dfca65.webm?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/fb4b3a8bfc4bed609c8f0b1853dfca65.mp4?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着夜幕降临，暗影开始苏醒，骇人的贪婪生物也将袭击你的王国。召集军队、鼓起勇气、磨练自己，因为每一晚都要求你不断增长自身的战术技巧。部署弓箭手、骑士、攻城武器，甚至是新获得的君主能力和神器，来抵御贪婪生物的浪潮。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/5f069648b38e9d4e0088440e4cfe420a.poster.avif?t=1771343090\" width=1170 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/5f069648b38e9d4e0088440e4cfe420a.webm?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/5f069648b38e9d4e0088440e4cfe420a.mp4?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你作为一国之君，需要亲自率军攻击贪婪生物的源头，才能保护辖下诸岛。派遣你的部队，去与敌人交战。注意：请确保你的军队兵精粮足，因为贪婪生物不会不战而降。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/4d3ebf43781fcf6f030a6a6748da4fb2.poster.avif?t=1771343090\" width=1170 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/4d3ebf43781fcf6f030a6a6748da4fb2.webm?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701160/extras/4d3ebf43781fcf6f030a6a6748da4fb2.mp4?t=1771343090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《王国：两位君主》能带给玩家不断进化的游戏体验，包含几项免费的内容更新：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>幕府时代：</strong>这片土地的灵感来自日本封建时代的建筑和文化。化身强大的幕府将军或女武士，征召忍者，骑上神兽麒麟，率军作战，一面运筹帷幄，一面鏖战竹林深处的贪婪生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>死亡之地：</strong>深入王国的黑暗之地。化身哥特风恐怖动作角色扮演游戏《赤痕》中的碎片人米莉娅姆等独特的君主，获得相应的强大特性。骑上巨大的甲虫，布设陷阱；骑上诡异的不死生物，召唤障碍，阻止贪婪生物的侵袭；或者骑上《赤痕》神秘的恶魔生物加麦基，发动强大的冲刺攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战岛：</strong>对于久经沙场的老练君主来说，这是有史以来最大的挑战。迎接五项规则和目标各不相同的挑战。你能尽力活下来，并夺得金王冠吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的冒险才刚刚开始。在额外的DLC和游戏内容中，探索更多不为人知的故事和场景。君主啊，请保持警惕，因为黑夜就要来临，保护好你的王冠！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 俄语, 法语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西",
